caption.body: Milwaukee-based filmmaker Dave Kiehl employs traditional cut-out animation and watercolor painting with digital applications in this imaginative short in which a lumbering aircraft mechanically produces the creatures of an idyllic world below. See "The Seed in the Sky" by Dave Kiehl, now playing, in the Video Arts Room located pre-security in the International Terminal.
